# Load Factor Index Data
data = pd.concat([pd.read_csv(file) for file in tqdm(files) if Path(file).name.split("_")[0] in TICKERS.Ticker.values])
data = data.rename(lambda x: x.lower(), axis=1)
data.close = data.close.fillna(data["last price"])
data.date = pd.to_datetime(data.date)
data = data.rename({"sym_bbg": "sym"}, axis=1)[["date", "sym", "open", "high", "low", "close", "volume"]]

In [179]:
tpx500 = ['TPX Index', 'TPX500 Index', 'TPX500V Index', 'TPX500G Index']
pct_ret_1d = data.groupby(["date", "sym"]).close.last().unstack(level=-1).replace(0, np.nan).fillna(method="ffill").pct_change().mul(1e2)
display(pct_ret_1d[tpx500].corr().style.format(precision=3).background_gradient(vmin=0, vmax=1))

for horizon in ["1W", "1M", "1Q", "180d"]:
    prices = data.groupby(["date", "sym"]).close.last().unstack(level=-1).replace(0, np.nan).fillna(method="ffill")
    prices = prices.resample(horizon).last()
    display(horizon, prices.pct_change()[tpx500].corr().style.format(precision=3).background_gradient(vmin=0, vmax=1))
